            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Clara Neiman</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#neimanC" start="87.744" end="x">They were Russian [as it often happens, she identifies the Greek Orthodox religion with the Russian nationality]. And then they went over to Judaism.</span>
        </li>
