                <span class="">Clara Neiman</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#neimanC" start="130.180" end="x">Born Russians, who went over [to Judaism], but we . . . I still was not . . . but the other already [were born in Jewish faith]. I and my older brother, already deceased, were not born [as Jews]. A year of two before or later.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="138.442" end="x">And your mother.</span>
